{"tid":2403141,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"昨才向警投訴濫捕 有人稱上月收指控  早產婦斥PK鄧作古仔","createTime":"2021-02-11T02:29:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T03:28:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ae9f1188b93e57bb5fc617bb8491d00d76663cdd","tid":2403141,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:29:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210211/LSVD3SDA4NACTIURM45LDDETL4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210211%2FLSVD3SDA4NACTIURM45LDDETL4%2F&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLHqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=24f73ea6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210211%2FLSVD3SDA4NACTIURM45LDDETL4%2F&h=38d283f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210211/LSVD3SDA4NACTIURM45LDDETL4/</a><br />\n<br />\n昨才向警投訴濫捕 有人稱上月收指控 <br />\n早產婦斥PK鄧作古仔<br />\n<br />\n【時事聚焦】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】懷孕七個多月的孕婦疑受警暴對待致早產男嬰，事主劉女士昨到灣仔警察總部正式投訴，要求警方還原真相，並還自己公道。對於警務署署長鄧炳強早前回應事件時，否認涉事警務人員犯錯及使用不必要武力，她對鄧「未審先判」的言論表示不滿，更質疑他「作古仔」，難以感受他慰問的真誠。區議員形容事件「人神共憤」，要求警方道歉。<br />\n<br />\n劉女士直言，難以感受鄧炳強慰問的真誠，亦不滿他否認涉事警務人員犯錯，及指警員施以「最低武力」的說法；她又質疑，自己昨天才正式向警方投訴，但上月底鄧卻指已接獲投訴，對警方所指的「投訴人」大惑不解，有「作古仔」之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/skUUHJ3H8BiY6usoNQz0mBOOjB4=/1826x1024/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5D4YJ7XMUBAFLDTDHMQ2PACUZI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FskUUHJ3H8BiY6usoNQz0mBOOjB4%3D%2F1826x1024%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5D4YJ7XMUBAFLDTDHMQ2PACUZI.jpg&h=1daf4748&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■劉女士昨由區議員黎廣偉陪同到警總正式投訴遭警暴。<br />\n<br />\n子仍留醫插喉<br />\n<br />\n她稱投訴主要涉及四項，包括態度惡劣、濫用職權、疏忽職守及行為不當。警員初步為她錄口供「開file」，但未有接收載有兩段影片的usb。劉女士坦言不抱太大希望，形容警方調查不會達到公開公正，亦預料調查需時極長，但為討回公道，也要一試。離開警總，她立即到醫院探望兒子。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">「呢幾日佢係咁嘔奶，一掂佢就氣促，搞到氧氣箱係咁着燈，我都唔敢再掂佢。」數天前一個夜晚，院方突然致電劉女士，指其兒子發燒，達38℃高溫。醫生怕嬰兒患上腦膜炎，遂作脊椎穿刺檢查，她哽咽：「佢之後可能會行唔到，咁細個bb要打一針。」這令劉女士連夜失眠。</span><br />\n<br />\n現時劉女士的兒子因早產致發育不健全，僅靠氧氣箱呼吸，靠餵食管進食，體重只得1.63公斤。「佢插住條管好唔舒服，係咁用手整開條管，塊面紅晒，好辛苦。」她現時每周僅有三次30分鐘的探望機會，談到兒子時更一度聲淚俱下。<br />\n<br />\n陪同劉女士到警總的九龍城區議員黎廣偉形容事件「人神共憤」，批評警方以「最低智力」執行職務，「唔係話佢哋冇腦，而係被情緒主導，未有客觀嘅判斷」，要求警方向劉女士正式道歉。若今次投訴不獲接納，未來將作出法律行動，盡力為她爭取公道。<br />\n<br />\n今年1月20日，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Ddx153vgBi621M5HS3-lfcwcUI4=/1181x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/E3KEVK5HBZGHHOCL37ZDKGTDLE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDdx153vgBi621M5HS3-lfcwcUI4%3D%2F1181x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FE3KEVK5HBZGHHOCL37ZDKGTDLE.jpg&h=51493ef6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■劉女士兒子現仍需靠氧氣箱呼吸及餵食管進食。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/M2XXx3i8jA5OCtOk-2d9az6hG3k=/1395x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XJHFELS375AG5I4P33LWKUDDRY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FM2XXx3i8jA5OCtOk-2d9az6hG3k%3D%2F1395x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXJHFELS375AG5I4P33LWKUDDRY.jpg&h=98f67795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄧炳強"},{"pid":"73826f4517786ba8b002bcebeb3b03d1d615a03b","tid":2403141,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:30:09.000Z","msg":"此投訴不同彼投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88472a16954acbe82a93be783febf19d7457128c","tid":2403141,"uid":72185,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T03:02:12.000Z","msg":"屌鳩個仔未來老頂都有既<br />\n你個仔第時仲要做白警架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edca853e375078e32189881ff684af424f6b6387","tid":2403141,"uid":266354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T03:07:55.000Z","msg":"腦殘藍絲既報應 報落個仔到<br />\n運動個時呢d腦殘藍肯定大大聲屌後生仔<br />\n抵撚死"},{"pid":"8165b83a9c4880f39f9a873cb01caf7f699b09d7","tid":2403141,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T03:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed94cbabb25730bc0cfa3e06a658fe0b66816dd","tid":2403141,"uid":155682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T03:28:28.000Z","msg":"PK : 可能我講得唔清楚, 我係接到負責警員嘅投訴, 投訴阿大肚婆扮肥婆誤導警員及阻差辦公."}]}